creator: dua AG
descriptionHtml:
Our mission is to connect over 12 million Albanian people around the world. Dua.com connects Albanians from Kosovo with the ones from Switzerland, Germany with Albania, Macedonia with the UK and more!

Download the app and start searching for your partner anywhere, anytime and meet them in real life. Our app helps you connect in these simple ways:

- Easy login. Sign up with e-mail, phone number or Facebook. Start connecting with new people for free.
- Set the location you are interested in. Start exploring and choosing the partner you like.
- Optimize your profile - the more information you provide the better chances to find a perfect match.
- Start chatting and begin your journey to new meaningful relationships. No stress!

With thousands of active users - your chances of finding your Albanian match are stronger than ever.

Coming soon:
- dua.help - travelling to a foreign city, or just looking for new friends? Socialize with fellow Albanians worldwide in our help modus.
- dua.biz - have a business idea? Looking for a partner? Find potential investors, partners with our business modus.
descriptionShort: A new dating experience. Meet, chat and build strong relationships at any time.

descriptionHtml:
Our mission is to connect over 12 million Albanian people around the world. dua.com connects Albanians from Kosovo with the ones in Switzerland, Germany with Albania, Macedonia with the UK and more!

With thousands of active users - your chances of finding your Albanian match are stronger than ever.

Happy connecting!

Our mission is to connect over 12 million Albanians from all around the world in the fields of love, help, and biz! From Prishtina to Zürich, Berlin to Tirana, Skopje to London, Ulqin to New York, and more!

All you need to do is to download our app and create a profile right now!

Our app helps you connect in these simple ways:

- Easy login. Sign up with e-mail, phone number, or Facebook.
- Set the location you are interested in and start exploring!
- Optimize your profile - the more information you provide the better chances to find a perfect match!
- Verify your profile & connect it with Instagram!
- Start chatting and begin your journey to new meaningful relationships!

With thousands of daily active users - your chances of finding your Albanian match are stronger than ever!

Coming soon:
- dua.biz - Have a business idea? Looking for a partner? Find potential investors, partners with our business modus.
- dua.help - Traveling to a foreign city, or just looking for new friends? Socialize with fellow Albanians worldwide in our help modus.

title: dua.com - Connect with Albanians worldwide

creator: dua AG
descriptionHtml:
dua.com is an app created for Albanians wherever they are!

Whether you want to make meaningful connections, make new friends, connect with businesspeople and more, we’re here to help.

Match with new people from Zürich, Pristina, Berlin, New York, London etc, with just one click.

How to succeed in dua.com? Complete your profile. Easy as that! Just choose the best pictures you have, fill out your bio section, verify your account and start liking!

With thousands of daily active users, your chances of meeting your Albanian match have never been better!

WHAT IS DUA’S MISSION

Dua’s mission is to democratize the way globally fragmented communities connect by providing the Go-To platform for people to connect to their community through all kinds of relationships, which includes dating and meeting new business people and friends.

COOL DUA.COM FEATURES

A satisfied user is all that we care about, in the end, we are doing this for our dear Albanians :). Below is a list of the most used features that we currently have. We suggest that as soon as you download that app, give them a try!

- ‘Fly’ - Change your location with just one click
- ‘InstaChat’ - Send a personalized message, before matching (but you have to be verified first)
- ‘Photo Verification’ - We love & reward users who have a verified profile
- ‘Undo’ - Mistakes happen, but they can now easily be fixed
- ‘Video/Voice calls’ - When the topic is so good, it's easier to explain with a video call :)

SOME STATISTICS ABOUT DUA.COM

- Around 300’000 users are registered
- Around 100 success love stories that are known for us
- Communities from 33 countries (with more than 1’000 users)
- Made with love from Pristina & Tirana

COMING SOON:

- dua.biz - Have a business idea? Looking for a partner? Find potential investors & partners with our business model.
- dua.help - Traveling to a new place? Or just looking for friends? Socialize with Albanians worldwide with our help model.
- dua pay - A faster, safer, and more cost-efficient alternative to send, spend and save money, all in 1 simple account.

dua is free to download and use. However, we also offer optional subscription packages (dua Premium)

WHAT DOES DUA PREMIUM OFFER?

- More impressions
- Access the “Liked you” scree
- Unlimited flights
- More InstaChats
- Zero advertising
- Unlimited Undo
- Upload up to 6 photos
- Unlimited video chats/audio calls

We offer monthly, 3 months and 12-month subscriptions. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change without notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.

Payment will be charged to your Google account at confirmation of purchase.
Your subscription will automatically renew itself unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.

You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal by going to Payments & Subscriptions and then Subscription.

More Information

https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/7018481?hl=en&co=GENIE.Platform%3DAndroid#zippy=%2Ccancel-a-subscription-on-the-google-play-app

Your personal data is securely stored on dua - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions:

Terms of Service: https://www.dua.com/en/terms-and-conditions/
Privacy Policy: https://www.dua.com/en/privacy-policy/
FAQ: https://www.dua.com/faq/

All photos are of models and/or bought stock pictures and are used for illustrative purposes only.
descriptionShort: Connecting Albanians around the globe!

Hey there! We managed to fix a few performance issues within the app. We also smashed some bugs!

Oh, and yeah - happy connecting! :)

With thousands of daily active users, your chances of meeting your Albanian match have never been better!

WHAT IS DUA’S MISSION

Dua’s mission is to democratize the way globally fragmented communities connect by providing the Go-To platform for people to connect to their community through all kinds of relationships, which includes dating and meeting new business people and friends.

COOL DUA.COM FEATURES

A satisfied user is all that we care about, in the end, we are doing this for our dear Albanians :). Below is a list of the most used features that we currently have. We suggest that as soon as you download that app, give them a try!

- ‘Fly’ - Change your location with just one click
- ‘InstaChat’ - Send a personalized message, before matching (but you have to be verified first)
- ‘Photo Verification’ - We love & reward users who have a verified profile
- ‘Undo’ - Mistakes happen, but they can now easily be fixed
- ‘Video/Voice calls’ - When the topic is so good, it's easier to explain with a video call :)

SOME STATISTICS ABOUT DUA.COM

- Around 300’000 users are registered
- Around 100 success love stories that are known for us
- Communities from 33 countries (with more than 1’000 users)
- Made with love from Pristina & Tirana

COMING SOON:

- dua.biz - Have a business idea? Looking for a partner? Find potential investors & partners with our business model.
- dua.help - Traveling to a new place? Or just looking for friends? Socialize with Albanians worldwide with our help model.
- dua pay - A faster, safer, and more cost-efficient alternative to send, spend and save money, all in 1 simple account.

dua is free to download and use. However, we also offer optional subscription packages (dua Premium)

WHAT DOES DUA PREMIUM OFFER?

- More impressions
- Access the “Liked you” scree
- Unlimited flights
- More InstaChats
- Zero advertising
- Unlimited Undo
- Upload up to 6 photos
- Unlimited video chats/audio calls

We offer monthly, 3 months and 12-month subscriptions. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change without notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.

Payment will be charged to your Google account at confirmation of purchase.
Your subscription will automatically renew itself unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.

You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal by going to Payments & Subscriptions and then Subscription.

- ‘InstaChat’ - Send a personalized message, before matching (but you have to be verified first)

- ‘Undo’ - Mistakes happen, but they can now easily be fixed
- ‘Video/Voice calls’ - When the topic is so good, it's easier to explain with a video call :)

- Around 300’000 users are registered

WHAT DOES DUA PREMIUM OFFER?

- More impressions

- More InstaChats
- Zero advertising

We offer monthly, 3 months and 12-month subscriptions. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change without notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.

Payment will be charged to your Google account at confirmation of purchase.
Your subscription will automatically renew itself unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.

You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal by going to Payments & Subscriptions and then Subscription.

We have thousands of daily active users from around the world who are here to chat and date & meet up with each other from different cities like Zürich, Pristina, Berlin, New York, London, and anywhere around the world. It’s fun to match people with just one click!

Our mission is to democratize the way globally fragmented communities connect by providing a go-to platform to connect and match people to their community through all kinds of relationships. A dating app that allows you to make friends, chat and date, meet up and have a relationship in a way that makes you belong on dua.com.

Ditch the one-size-fits-all applications, and connect with your community to find a profound connection and make friends. Download the dating app to start a relationship, chat and date today 😁.

COMMUNITY-BASED DATING
Make friends meet up, connect, and match people around the US with Albanians and soon also with:

And so much more!

title: dua: Make Friends, Chat & Date

creator: dua AG
descriptionHtml:
Love is in the air! We are thrilled to welcome you to dua, a nationality-based dating app that promises meaningful connections and amazing opportunities for lasting relationships.

Looking for the one? Who has the same cultural background as you? Who speaks the same language? Well, perfect; you are in the right place!

We stand for:
Celebrating the many different Human Experiences.

- Nationality (Origin, Culture & Language)
- Family
- Union of Men and Women

dua attracts confident women & men who celebrate their uniqueness, culture, values, language and roots through their bold fashion, cuisine, music and individual perspective of life!

Women & Men who join dua are not afraid to stand for something and to stand out from the crowd and celebrate their exotic differences.

Some statistics:
- 137 different nationalities.
- Around 500,000 registered users.
- Over 10'000 successful love stories.
- Users from 155 countries.

Image verification is an important step in protecting our community, which we encourage every user to go through.

Core Features:

- ‘Fly’ – Change your location with just one click!
- ‘InstaChat’ – Send a direct message before matching
- 'Boost' - Get more visibility for a 30 minutes period
- 'Video/Voice calls’ – When the conversation is so good, it's easier to keep it going with a video call

Which Nationalities does dua support?
All of them!

Here are just some of them listed:
- Ukrainians
- Bosnians
- Turkish
- Croatians
- Albanians
- Romanians
- Swedish
- Serbians
- Germans

Everyone is welcome!

COMING SOON IN DUA APP

- duaBiz: Have a business idea? Looking for a partner? Find potential investors & partners on dua.com!
- duaFriends: Traveling to a new place? Or just looking for friends? Socialize with your nationality worldwide!

Also:
dua has created a token called DUA Token, which will be used to reward the community for its nonstop work of keeping the community safe. For more details please visit our website.

We also offer optional subscription packages with dua Premium.

dua Premium

- Get more impressions on your profile
- Get more boosts
- Access the “Liked you” screen
- Get unlimited flights for when you’re on the go
- Get access to more InstaChats
- Ad-Free dua.com experience
- Get Unlimited Undo’s
- Upload up to 6 photos
- Unlimited video chats/audio calls

We offer monthly, 3-month, and 12-month subscriptions. Prices are displayed in the app. Payment will be charged to your Google account at confirmation of purchase.
Your subscription will automatically renew itself unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

Your account will be charged for renewal 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal by going to Payments & Subscriptions and then Subscription.

descriptionHtml:
You are Albanian, Moroccan, Turk? You want to chat with people who share your origin? Well, then it's time for you to download our dating app! Albanian dating app, Moroccan dating app, and for many others! Regardless of your ethnicity, Albanian, Moroccan or Turk, members of ethnic communities coming from mass emigration can’t find people who share their origin within the new country they’ve chosen to settle down. E.g. Albanians living about 50% outside their home countries.

dua.com's mission is to reconnect those people again and make it possible for them to create a new relationship. We believe that dating the right person and creating a healthy relationship deserve our full attention, love, focus, and energy. So, wherever you are, if dating within your ethnicity is what you are looking for, dua.com is for you!

Enjoy our app with many cool basic features:

- "Fly" to a new location: You are an Albanian living in NY? With the Fly feature, you may find your other Albanian half wherever in the world! ✈️
- Video Chat enables you to experience a live chat with your other half, no matter your distance! 🤳
- To shy to start a video chat? Then our Instachat is the right thing. Start the chat without waiting for a match ;) 💌
- Verified users: No need to worry who you are talking to. Our users are verified ✅

Not enough yet? dua.com Premium offers unlimited possibilities:

- Find out who likes you 💖
- Boost your profile to gain more attention ⚡
- Get unlimited "InstaChat" and much more 💌

Download dua.com NOW and enjoy the following benefits:

- EASY SIGN-UP - register with email, phone number, or Facebook
- SET LOCATION - set your location and start searching
- OPTIMIZE PROFILE - more information mean greater chances to find the perfect partner
- VERIFY PROFILE - confirm your profile and link it to Instagram
- GET STARTED - start chatting and enjoy your journey to a new meaningful relationship

We use advanced matchmaking algorithms to connect people based on origin and values to create a meaningful and long-lasting relationship without any doubt. Choose your own origin, the ethnicity you belong to, and find, chat & meet people who speak your language and share your values.

At dua.com you may find users from 50+ different ethnic communities. Our fastest-growing user bases are Albanians, Moroccans and Turks, followed by Germans, Syrians, Polish people, Italians and many Balkan-based communities.

If you are looking for an Albanian dating app, want to meet Moroccan singles, or date Turkish people or any other ethnic community - then dua.com is the right place!

Therefore join us, meet new people and create a long-lasting relationship.

Experience dating differently!

Love is … finding someone who shares your dreams and values! Connect with people worldwide and discover what real love is about. With our Spotted feature, fate brings you together! Get a notification when you’ve met someone in real life, sparking a chance for a meaningful connection. Maybe even your true love! Find people and let your shared interests and diverse backgrounds create a beautiful romance. Whether you’re in Germany or seeking a partner from Albania, Italy, Switzerland, or elsewhere, our platform is where your dating journey begins!

At dua.com real love awaits! And our goal is to unite people in search of their soulmate. Your ex-partners were not meant to be. Don't lose hope though - your perfect partner is out there, now waiting for you! Start dating and meet your soulmate for the relationship you've been dreaming of. Our new Feature Spotted is been designed to help your find people you have crossed paths with in real time. Find them again in our diverse community from all over to chat and connect and discover more than just a companion - find your perfect match!


What is it though that sets us apart as a dating app?

- Members from over 150 countries: Germany, Albania, Türkiye, Switzerland, and many more.

- Spotted someone? Discover and connect with people you've seen nearby in real time. Maybe it was your partner i crime you have just missed.

- Get personal recommendations with our “Recommended Match of the Day” feature: increase your chances of meeting your true love

- Flight Feature: Find people who share your origins in other place and get to know them

- Advanced filters: Real love also means knowing what you want. Search and find your soulmate based on location, interests, nationality, and much more.

creator: dua AG
descriptionHtml:
Meet & Date Albanians Worldwide with dua.com - The (only) Albanian Dating App

Join over 900,000 Albanians worldwide on dua.com!

Whether in Kosovo, Albania, or in Diaspora, connect with Albanians who share your values, traditions, culture, language, and jokes.

WHY CHOOSE DUA.COM?
- Exclusively for Albanians
- Verified Profiles: Engage only with real users - verification is now mandatory when you register on dua.com.
- Spotted Feature: Reconnect with Albanians you've crossed paths with anywhere in the world.
- Flight Feature: Change your location and meet Albanians in your desired city.
- Advanced Filters: Find your one love by filtering for important things to you, such as height, religion, language, etc.

OUR MISSION
As proud Albanians, our mission is to preserve the Albanian DNA by building strong, healthy families. We are dedicated to protecting our values like Besa, our traditions, and our language, empowering Albanians to reach their full potential.

OUR VISION
BE – Be the one. Be the best version of yourself.
FIND – Find the one. Your one. Your way. (The current app experience)
GROW – Grow together. Supporting couples to build strong, healthy Albanian families.

WHO SHOULD USE DUA.COM?
- Albanians everywhere seek to find love and build a family with someone who shares their values and culture.

SAFETY IS EXTREMELY IMPORTANT TO US
- 100% Verified Users: Every user must verify their profile during sign-up to ensure a safe community.
- Block Contacts: Block people from your contact list.
- Spotted Control: Add locations where you won’t appear via the Spotted feature.

FOR HER: EXTRA SAFE FEATURES
- Hide My Photos: Choose to hide your photos until you're ready to share them with the public.
- Incognito Mode: Only people you like can see your profile.

LOVE BEYOND BORDERS
dua.com makes it easy to connect with Albanians, no matter where you are. Whether you’re dating in New York, Zurich, or Tirana, find people who share your culture and values.

EXPERIENCE DUA PREMIUM
Enhance your experience with dua Premium and enjoy these exclusive features:

- See Who Liked You: View all your admirers in one place.
- Unlimited Likes: Explore endless connections with no limits.
- InstaChats: Send messages before matching.
- Undo: Reverse your last swipe and give someone a second chance.
- Flight Feature: Change your location to connect globally.
- Monthly Boost: Boost your profile to the top for 30 minutes for more visibility.

You can use dua.com for free without subscribing to dua Premium.

All photos are models, used for illustrative purposes only.
